# Member 2 — UI + Admin Dashboard + Version Control

Build the main React frontend for the **Last-Mile Scanner PWA**, covering all navigation pages and an admin dashboard, plus version control documentation.

## Proposed Changes

### React App Setup (Vite)

#### [NEW] Project root at `d:\Frontend UI\parcel-tracker\`

Initialize a Vite + React app. Install:
- `react-router-dom` — client-side routing
- `recharts` — charts for admin dashboard
- `lucide-react` — icon set

---

### Design System

#### [NEW] `src/index.css`
Global CSS with:
- Dark mode palette (deep navy, electric blue, accent green)
- Typography (Inter font from Google Fonts)
- CSS custom properties (tokens)
- Smooth animations / transitions

#### [NEW] `src/components/Layout.jsx`
Sidebar with links to all 4 main pages + dedicated Admin section.

---

### Main Pages (`src/pages/`)

#### [NEW] `ScanPage.jsx`
- QR/barcode scan UI with animated scan zone
- Recent scans list fed from mock data
- Status indicators (success / pending / failed)

#### [NEW] `DeliveryPage.jsx`
- Active deliveries list with agent name, status badge, ETA
- Mark delivered / in-transit actions (UI only)
- Search and filter bar

#### [NEW] `WarehousePage.jsx`
- Warehouse capacity card with live-style progress bar
- Parcel count display
- Camera feed placeholder (ready for ML integration)

#### [NEW] `PaymentPage.jsx`
- Payment form: amount, mode (UPI/Cash/Card)
- Recent transactions table
- Mismatch alert display for cash difference

---

### Admin Dashboard (`src/pages/admin/`)

#### [NEW] `AdminLayout.jsx`
Dedicated admin sidebar with accent styling.

#### [NEW] `DeliveryLogs.jsx`
- Table of all delivery events (parcel ID, agent, time, status)
- Filter by status / date
- `recharts` BarChart summary

#### [NEW] `LocationLogs.jsx`
- Table of GPS location captures (agent, lat, lng, timestamp)
- Last-known location highlighted

#### [NEW] `PaymentStatus.jsx`
- Table of payment records (order ID, amount, mode, status)
- `recharts` PieChart for payment mode breakdown
- Mismatch rows highlighted in red

---

### Version Control Documentation

#### [NEW] `d:\Frontend UI\README.md`
Project overview, setup instructions, team structure.

#### [NEW] `d:\Frontend UI\BRANCHING_STRATEGY.md`
Branching strategy:
- `main` → stable production
- `develop` → integration branch
- `feature/<name>` → per-member features
- `hotfix/<name>` → urgent production fixes

#### [NEW] `d:\Frontend UI\.gitignore`
Standard Node.js / React gitignore.

---

## Verification Plan

### Automated Dev Server Test
```
cd "d:\Frontend UI\parcel-tracker"
npm run dev
```
Confirm the app starts without errors on `http://localhost:5173`.

### Manual Navigation Test
1. Open `http://localhost:5173` in browser
2. Click **Scan** in sidebar → Scan page loads with animated scan zone
3. Click **Delivery** → Delivery page loads with list
4. Click **Warehouse** → Warehouse page loads with capacity bar
5. Click **Payment** → Payment form visible
6. Click **Admin → Delivery Logs** → Table with mock data renders
7. Click **Admin → Location Logs** → GPS table renders
8. Click **Admin → Payment Status** → Table + PieChart renders

### Browser Recording
A browser subagent will navigate the live app and record a walkthrough video.
